"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the"
" model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的功能](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)以获取该模型支持的功能矩阵。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/LLaVA-OneVision-Qwen2-0.5B-OV.md:13
