#: ../../source/tutorials/models/LLaVA-OneVision-Qwen2-0.5B-OV.md:21
msgid ""
"The verified single-card deployment uses one Atlas A2 NPU. It is "
"recommended to cache model weights under `/root/.cache` in advance to "
"reduce startup time."
msgstr ""
"已验证的单卡部署使用一个 Atlas A2 NPU。建议提前将模型权重缓存到 `/root/.cache` 目录下，以减少启动时间。"

